---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <h1><span class="prompt">$</span> whoami</h1>

  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="terminal-block">
      <div class="terminal-header">
        <span class="dot red"></span>
        <span class="dot yellow"></span>
        <span class="dot green"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">user@verification-hell</span>
      </div>
      <div class="terminal-body">
        <p><span class="prompt">$</span> cat ~/.profile</p>
        <pre class="output">
NAME="Clint Phillips"
LOCATION="Atlanta, GA"
STATUS="Clearing Resentments, One Post at a Time"
MOOD="Therapeutically Unhinged"
RECOVERY="One Day at a Time"
        </pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Why This Blog Exists</h2>
    
    <p>
      I'm Clint. I'm in recovery, and one of the things they teach you in AA 
      is that holding onto resentments is like drinking poison and expecting 
      the other person to die. The healthy thing is to let them go.
    </p>

    <p>
      But first, I'm going to write them all down. Publicly. With receipts.
    </p>

    <p>
      This blog is my therapeutic outlet for every corporation that's wronged me, 
      every contractor who's screwed me over, and every faceless system that's 
      made my life harder than it needed to be. Consider it a public service 
      for anyone researching companies before doing business with them.
    </p>

    <h2>What You'll Find Here</h2>
    
    <ul>
      <li>Detailed accounts of corporate nightmares</li>
      <li>Contractor horror stories (with names named)</li>
      <li>Screenshots, receipts, and documentation</li>
      <li>The occasional dark humor</li>
      <li>Hopefully, some catharsis</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    
    <p>
      Got your own horror story? Want to commiserate? 
      Or maybe you're from one of the companies I've written about 
      and want to make things right? (Unlikely, but I'm an optimist.)
    </p>

    <div class="contact-info">
      <p><span class="label">Email:</span> clint@technolo.co</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-content {
    max-width: 100%;
  }

  .terminal-block {
    background: var(--bg-terminal);
    border: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
    border-radius: 6px;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .terminal-header {
    background: #2d2d2d;
    padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #444;
  }

  .dot {
    width: 12px;
    height: 12px;
    border-radius: 50%;
  }

  .dot.red { background: #ff5f56; }
  .dot.yellow { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .dot.green { background: #27ca40; }

  .terminal-title {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: #888;
  }

  .terminal-body {
    padding: 1rem;
  }

  .terminal-body p {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: #00ff41;
  }

  .terminal-body .output {
    color: #8be9fd;
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .terminal-body .prompt {
    color: #ff79c6;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    padding: 1rem;
    border-radius: 4px;
    border: 2px solid var(--border-strong);
  }

  .contact-info p {
    margin: 0.5rem 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .contact-info .label {
    color: var(--accent);
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
